      "notes": "组件族（Tabs、TabsList、TabsTrigger、TabsIndicator、TabsContent）基于 Ark UI Tabs 原语封装。样式覆盖通过各组件 class prop 实现，不提供 ui 或 ui.* 配置入口。"
    },
    "capabilities": [
      "v-model",
      "theme",
      "orientation",
      "lazy-mount",
      "composite-item"
    ],
    "subComponents": ["TabsList", "TabsTrigger", "TabsIndicator", "TabsContent"]
  },
